00:03:11.340 --> 00:03:12.215
So of course, we did.

00:03:12.215 --> 00:03:15.920
And up came the information
about game three of the 1937

00:03:15.920 --> 00:03:16.709
World Series.

00:03:16.709 --> 00:03:18.500
Not that long ago, I
